{"tid":776133,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼亂煮]—紅桑子棉花糖 Raspberries Marshmallow","createTime":"2018-08-11T18:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T19:07:02.000Z","uid":182683,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"857f3a3520f97fd0a3faed05b81eef0004a723db","tid":776133,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"Ig Story有片同埋我把真聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n今日依個甜品我整完都先發覺有啲複雜同埋要有攪拌機先整到，所以如果真係整嘅話有咩唔明問清楚我先，唔整都冇所謂，就當娛樂下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/020008_ec89dc84bf6772a1f4cce781891025c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F020008_ec89dc84bf6772a1f4cce781891025c6.png&h=4df0ab49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請買啲新鮮靚嘅紅桑子，如果買左啲差野係會整都整唔到。同埋個甜品比較甜同淨係放到2日，唔係鍾意食甜野就考慮下先整或者整比人食。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n材料：<br />\n白糖 300g <br />\n栗膠60g (liquid glucose)<br />\n水 90g ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n蛋白 90g<br />\n白糖 90g<br />\n魚膠片 15g (我用個隻一塊等於5g，睇清楚包裝寫幾多g，唔好用磅個重量）<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n雲喱拿油 2茶匙 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n新鮮紅桑子 400g <br />\n糖霜 如有需要 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n做法： <br />\n1.處理紅桑子<br />\n紅桑子買買靚少少(通常超市放個架最後個啲係新鮮啲)，如果唔靚個啲整個時會出水同爛，成個棉花糖會好濕。<br />\n淨係用實淨個啲，爛同出水嘅唔要，簡好曬千其唔好洗，用張紙抹抹就可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015428_2ed4516fee95cb8dd81e0416ed4394c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015428_2ed4516fee95cb8dd81e0416ed4394c0.png&h=e8a25d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.磅其他材料,準備材料同用具<br />\n白糖,栗膠,水拎個煲磅；蛋白放攪拌碗，糖同雲喱拿油分開用細蹀仔磅；魚膠片浸凍水備用。<br />\n用油掃個盤(2cm高x25cm長x19cm闊,我依個盤會整唔曬淨左少少出黎)，鋪張長過個盤一半嘅保鮮紙，再掃油。<br />\n魚膠片浸到軟身就拎起揸走啲水，放落第隻碗叮溶佢(唔好叮太熱會用唔到)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015536_c1a347516c78cbdc3214efe5a1f2b0a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015536_c1a347516c78cbdc3214efe5a1f2b0a1.png&h=6152f878&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015537_1282fb64b19dbecb8ec67cf915701c37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015537_1282fb64b19dbecb8ec67cf915701c37.png&h=412728fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.整棉花糖<br />\n糖個煲野開大火煮；同一時間開中慢速打蛋白，開始有泡見唔到底落一半糖，打到有少少紋落埋剩低個啲，轉中速打。<br />\n當煲糖煮到140&deg;C，機轉中慢速，慢慢倒啲糖漿入蛋白到，倒完就將溶左嘅魚膠倒埋落去，開最快打到個攪拌碗底摸落唔熱微暖(我打左15分鐘)，你會見到啲棉花糖好杰，啲紋路好清楚。<br />\n停機等到啲棉花糖完全唔熱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015643_296b39b7884872c2fbe79115911c6a58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015643_296b39b7884872c2fbe79115911c6a58.png&h=123eec1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015644_d596a82a9918d565a139f27214743485.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015644_d596a82a9918d565a139f27214743485.png&h=41d8598a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.撈紅桑子入棉花糖<br />\n棉花糖唔熱就可以撈啲紅桑子入去，依個步驟要好小心，盡量唔好整爛啲紅桑子。搽啲油落隻手到，倒曬啲紅桑子落個攪拌碗到，用手打轉咁由底攪啲棉花糖上黎冚住啲紅桑子撈，大概混沌就好停，攪太多下啲紅桑子會出水。<br />\n5.落盤鋪平<br />\n所有用具都要搽左油先用，用膠刮舀啲棉花糖落個盤到，盡量推向四隻角，舀滿左再用抹刀推平。<br />\n包好放雪櫃雪一日。 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015834_db45fb1835ed05eca1465b9deda308bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015834_db45fb1835ed05eca1465b9deda308bb.png&h=5d0eb4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.切棉花糖<br />\n又係所有用具搽左油先，成底連保鮮紙拎出黎，打直切左條先，再打橫切一粒粒，如果把刀太多野痴住就用紙抹乾淨再掃油先再切。<br />\n切完想靚啲又唔怕甜嘅撒少少糖霜，食得！<br />\n放雪櫃可以擺2日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015928_15cf063fda1196c380a56c79ad653169.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015928_15cf063fda1196c380a56c79ad653169.png&h=f03eddde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015929_0b4d330e4fe4427a4caead8700238693.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015929_0b4d330e4fe4427a4caead8700238693.png&h=ab38fd07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015930_8c23564d89ca4c34dc045ba2a629eb0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015930_8c23564d89ca4c34dc045ba2a629eb0e.png&h=ded3e343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依隻棉花糖因爲要放新鮮berries入去，所以加左蛋白令到佢冇咁硬身，唔係一般個隻比較煙韌嘅口感，而且只可以放2日，不過你整比甜甜星嘅囡囡應該好快食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n紅桑子嘅酸味完全平均到棉花糖個隻偏甜味，沖杯茶食正到！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost&d=7TYmk9QvXJAnk%2BOrP1FAaQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ba1d28c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6c4c7a83116d1d5a24e1ecfb78ccc6ba3dd989","tid":776133,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"次次咁夜出po唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8c44c393831bab12d1def585d5f5a22133602d","tid":776133,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 